-- Apple shares down after iPad sales data
-- 
-- Mon Apr 5, 2010 8:45am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2010/04/05/us-markets-stocks-beforethebell-apple-idUSTRE6341U820100405

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Shares of Apple Inc ( AAPL.O ) edged 0.8 percent lower to $234 in premarket trading on Monday after the company said it had sold over 300,000 units of its new iPad tablet computer on its first day of release, including deliveries of pre-ordered iPads. 

 (Reporting by  Ryan Vlastelica , Editing by W Simon )